quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  21,73,"And We made them imams, guiding according to Our Command. And We revealed unto them the doing of good deeds, the performance of prayer, and the giving of alms. And they were worshippers of Us"
  21,74,"And as for Lot, We gave unto him judgment and knowledge, and We saved him from the town that was committing vile deeds. Truly they were an evil people, iniquitous"
  21,75,"And We caused him to enter Our Mercy; verily, he was among the righteous"
  21,76,"And [remember] Noah, when he cried out aforetime, We answered him and saved him and his family from great distress"
  21,77,And We helped him against those people who denied Our signs. Truly they were an evil people; so We drowned them all together
  21,78,"And [remember] David and Solomon, when they rendered judgment regarding the tillage, when the peopleâ€™s sheep strayed therein by night. And We were Witness to their judgment"
  21,79,"We made Solomon to understand it, and unto both We gave judgment and knowledge. We compelled the mountains and the birds to glorify along with David; We did this"
  21,80,"And We taught him how to make garments for you to protect you against your own might, but are you thankful"
  21,81,"And unto Solomon, the wind blowing violently: it ran by his command to the land that We had blessed. And We know all things"